	in another pretty messed up tree ;)

2006-03-25  Michael Natterer  <mitch@gimp.org>

	* tools/pdbgen/pdb/brush.pdb
	* tools/pdbgen/pdb/brushes.pdb
	* tools/pdbgen/pdb/channel.pdb
