	* tools/pdbgen/app.pl: unconditionally initialize all return
	values, and don't initialize any parameter.

	* tools/pdbgen/pdb/*.pdb: removed init => 1 from all arguments
	and return values.

	* app/pdb/*_cmds.c: regenerated.

