	* app/gui/gui.c (gui_sanity_check): depend on gtk+ >= 2.8.8 also
	at runtime. We don't want to debug everybody's gtk problems...

2006-01-05  Sven Neumann  <sven@gimp.org>

	* configure.in: depend on gtk+ >= 2.8.8 (see bug #325794).

